title: New Oce Youtuber
body:
Hi there, Just starting out and would like some feed back.

Ive got some more videos planned and im editing them now but i just thought id put this out there anyway.

If anyone else out there has a youtube channel and wanted to colab or something feel free to message me.

replies.body:
I'd be happy to give you some tips and tricks, if you're thinking about getting serious in regards to content creation.

My channel; https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfEVeEAVPKFeliKnRCsq1xw
